metadata.name: Spiral Passage
metadata.description:
When worlds touch, interlinkedness happens.
The two fantasy worlds intertwine to form a stunning synergy, combining daydreams and bittersweet nostalgia.
Usually empty worlds gain observers and are filled with a wild outburst of life and action, exploring and manifesting themselves.
A transitional period, sparkling in fantasies, dreams and memories, consuming and generating itself like a looped helix.
This is the Spiral Passage.
